<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109751>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Gilpinia infuscalae Wang & Wei, sp. nov. A. Female, dorsal view. B. Male, lateral view. C. Female head, dorsal view. D. Female, mesoscutum, dorsal view. E. Female, metascutellum and tergum 1–3, dorsal-lateral view. F. Female, mesopleuron, lateral view. G. Ovipositor sheath, dorsal view. H. Scope of ovipositor sheath, ventral view. I. Lances. J. Lancet. K. 5–7th serrulae of lancet. L. Gonoforceps. M. Penis valve. Scale bars: 1–2 = 1 mm; 9 = 500 µm; 10–13 = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109751/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109755>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Lancets. A. Gilpinia baiyinaobaoa. B. G. fennica. C. G. virens. D. G. massoniana. E. G. yongrenica. F. G. pinicola. G. G. tohi. H. G. infuscalae sp. nov. I. G. tabulaeformis. J. G. hebedentata. K. G. jinghongensis. L. G. jingxii. M. G. lipuensis. N. G. nigra. A–G, I–M: Drawings of lancet by Xiao (1992), Xiao et al. (1992) and Xu (1997); N, photo by DRS." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109755/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

